    "7405369": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Choiseul",
                    "T": "Raimondo, during our last meeting, did I really mention that we must keep the public informed about the rebuilding of the institute with the utmost transparency?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Choiseul",
                    "T": "I really don't remember that. Perhaps I should check for it in the meeting notes. Could you tell me what page it was exactly?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "If by \"checking for it in the meeting notes,\" you mean you wish to see this point made in clear writing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "Then I must say that it won't happen, as such a point cannot be summarized into a single sentence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "This point was made based on the overall essence of that meeting, which was to first address morality and human relations, and the sum total of social norms..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "Lastly, this concept, when extracted from countless specific words and actions, is so broad and generic that anyone can see and comprehend its abstract concept."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Choiseul",
                    "T": "So what you're saying is, \"I didn't say that?\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "Uh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "Correct."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7405370": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Raimondo",
        "Step": "The Arkhium has finally been stabilized and the crisis resolved. You follow Raimondo back to the Fontaine Research Institute. As for Nacker's whereabouts and status, and the real reason why the institute handled the Central Laboratory the way it did... Should you tell the truth?",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "Finally, it's stabilized. The Arkhium has transformed into an inert state... We and the Fontaine Research Institute are safe, for now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But it seems there are ever more secrets."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "As for the things you'd like to know, I will happy to answer. But... not right now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "What I can tell you now, based on my hypothesis, is that... Mr. Nacker stole the Arkhium Kinetic Core and triggered this small explosion."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "But before explaining in too much detail, we should return to the Institute, and place the proper notation and partitions into this interlude."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "...Or at the very least, we need to stop Miss Journalist from getting more deeply involved. The Arkhium Kinetic Core is connected to too many other matters, and we must handle it in complete confidentiality."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "So, I would like you to \"cooperate\" with my work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Cooperate with your work?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Paimon",
                    "T": "You... you're not saying to play along with your lies, are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Paimon",
                    "T": "The scarier something is, the more you should share it with others! Then, we can all work together to deal with it faster!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "I have my doubts about that, you two. Every matter has its own way of being dealt with, and in this instance, we must first call for silence."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "But I promise that I would never have you steer from your moral standards or demand that you... have the same standard of behavior as we do."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "All I ask is for you to remain quiet. You need not do anything else. You might be wondering why I would have you remain silent while telling you the truth."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "I'll just come out and say it now. Your coming here is the only good fortune that our Institute has had in nearly a hundred years."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "No matter what happens or what the cost is, we must maintain good relations with you. I'm sure Mr. Choiseul feels the same way."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is telling the truth also a \"cost\" as far as you're concerned?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Is transparency something you'd consider a \"cost\" as well?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Paimon",
                    "T": "Yeah! You're only just telling us the truth now, which you should have done ages ago. Just what sorta \"cost\" is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "#Dear {M#sir}{F#lady}, Paimon. Telling the truth honestly is, in truth, the greatest price one can pay."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Raimondo",
                    "T": "Let's go back. I ask sincerely for your understanding and to provide all... necessary cooperation."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
